{"id":2206,"date":"2020-07-01T10:21:41","date_gmt":"2020-07-01T10:21:41","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/?page_id=2206"},"modified":"2024-07-04T10:28:44","modified_gmt":"2024-07-04T03:28:44","slug":"privacy-policy-vi","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/privacy-policy-vi\/","title":{"rendered":"Ch\u00ednh S\u00e1ch B\u1ea3o M\u1eadt"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><style><\/style><script type=\"text\/javascript\"><\/script><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-7q0kr1a6 fg-image  img-responsive full-width hidden-xs fg-text-dark\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/CSR-banner.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/01bc841934b89eff8df3cb7b33a193d6_CSR-banner-320-c-100.jpg 320w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/01bc841934b89eff8df3cb7b33a193d6_CSR-banner-768-c-100.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/01bc841934b89eff8df3cb7b33a193d6_CSR-banner-992-c-100.jpg 992w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/01bc841934b89eff8df3cb7b33a193d6_CSR-banner-1200-c-100.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/CSR-banner.jpg\" alt=\"CSR-banner\"><style><\/style><script type=\"text\/javascript\"><\/script><section class=\"ffb-id-48t2hql7 fg-section fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"fg-container container fg-container-large fg-container-lvl--1 \"><div class=\"fg-row row    \" ><div class=\"ffb-id-48t2hql8 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><h1 class=\"ffb-id-48t2hqlb fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\">CH\u00cdNH S\u00c1CH B\u1ea2O M\u1eacT<\/h1><div class=\"ffb-id-48t2hqlc fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">CARAVELLE SAIGON s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cookie \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch t&igrave;m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th&ocirc;ng tin m&agrave; Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch y&ecirc;u c\u1ea7u. \"Cookies\" l&agrave; chu\u1ed7i v\u0103n b\u1ea3n m&agrave; m\u1ed9t trang web truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d&ugrave;ng. C&aacute;c cookie(s) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh l&agrave; v&ocirc; danh, n&oacute; kh&ocirc;ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 danh t&iacute;nh c&aacute; nh&acirc;n hay theo d&otilde;i c&aacute;c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng tr&ecirc;n m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng website, v&agrave; c\u0169ng kh&ocirc;ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eef li\u1ec7u c&aacute; nh&acirc;n.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Thay v&agrave;o \u0111&oacute;, nh\u1eefng cookie s\u1ebd thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp cho t\u1eebng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d&ugrave;ng m\u1ed9t h&igrave;nh th\u1ee9c hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb ph&ugrave; h\u1ee3p, cho ph&eacute;p c&aacute;c m&aacute;y ch\u1ee7 cung c\u1ea5p ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c c&aacute;c khung h&igrave;nh v&agrave; n\u1ed9i dung tr&ecirc;n webiste. Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i kh&ocirc;ng c\u1ea7n th&ocirc;ng tin c&aacute; nh&acirc;n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d&ugrave;ng m&agrave; ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung v&agrave;o l&agrave;m sao \u0111\u1ec3 truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i th&ocirc;ng tin ph&ugrave; h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i theo d&otilde;i t&igrave;nh tr\u1ea1ng trang web \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed5i theo nhu c\u1ea7u kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i ch&uacute; &yacute; \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng th&ocirc;ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y&ecirc;u c\u1ea7u v&agrave; l&agrave;m cho s\u1ef1 t&igrave;m ki\u1ebfm d\u1ec5 d&agrave;ng h\u01a1n. B\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 d\u1eef li\u1ec7u n&agrave;o thu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n&agrave;y ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai kh&aacute;c tr\u1eeb khi quy \u0111\u1ecbnh r&otilde; r&agrave;ng t\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ee5p. N\u1ebfu Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch kh&ocirc;ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn c&aacute;c cookies, Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&oacute; th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp tr&igrave;nh duy\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a m&igrave;nh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i cookie (tham kh\u1ea3o h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn cho tr&igrave;nh duy\u1ec7t c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 c&aacute;ch l&agrave;m), m\u1eb7c d&ugrave; c&oacute; th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c&aacute;c giao d\u1ecbch nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh tr&ecirc;n trang web.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Trong M\u1eabu Th&ocirc;ng Tin \u0110\u1eb7t Ph&ograve;ng, ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i cung c\u1ea5p t&iacute;nh n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1eb7t ph&ograve;ng tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec3 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1eb7t ph&ograve;ng d\u1ec5 d&agrave;ng h\u01a1n. Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i t&ocirc;n tr\u1ecdng quy\u1ec1n b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch v&agrave; duy tr&igrave; th&ocirc;ng tin c&aacute; nh&acirc;n tr&ecirc;n m&aacute;y ch\u1ee7 m\u1ed9t c&aacute;ch an to&agrave;n v&agrave; tuy\u1ec7t m\u1eadt. Ch\u1ec9 c&oacute; Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch m\u1edbi c&oacute; quy\u1ec1n truy c\u1eadp, duy tr&igrave; v&agrave; s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. KH&Aacute;CH S\u1ea0N CARAVELLE kh&ocirc;ng \u1ee7y quy\u1ec1n cho b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh&aacute;c c\u1ee7a th&ocirc;ng tin b&iacute; m\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">S\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p c&oacute; li&ecirc;n quan \u0111\u1ebfn th&ocirc;ng tin th\u1ebb t&iacute;n d\u1ee5ng, t&ecirc;n, \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9, e-mail c\u1ee7a Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch v&agrave; b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th&ocirc;ng tin c&aacute; nh&acirc;n kh&aacute;c, Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&oacute; th\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p trong M\u1eabu Th&ocirc;ng Tin \u0110\u1eb7t Ph&ograve;ng c\u1ee7a trang web m\u1ed9t c&aacute;ch an to&agrave;n.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">S\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p c&oacute; li&ecirc;n quan \u0111\u1ebfn th&ocirc;ng tin th\u1ebb t&iacute;n d\u1ee5ng, t&ecirc;n, \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9, e-mail c\u1ee7a Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch v&agrave; b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th&ocirc;ng tin c&aacute; nh&acirc;n kh&aacute;c, Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&oacute; th\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p th&ocirc;ng tin trong M\u1eabu Th&ocirc;ng Tin \u0110\u1eb7t Ph&ograve;ng c\u1ee7a trang web m\u1ed9t b&ecirc;n th\u1ee9 ba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li&ecirc;n k\u1ebft tr&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n trang web c\u1ee7a ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i, tuy nhi&ecirc;n h\u1ecd c&oacute; nh\u1eefng ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch thu th\u1eadp d\u1eef li\u1ec7u ri&ecirc;ng bi\u1ec7t, ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; tr&aacute;ch nhi\u1ec7m ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ecbu tr&aacute;ch nhi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch hay ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a b&ecirc;n th\u1ee9 ba.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><style>.ffb-id-48t2hql7{ padding-top: 50px;padding-right: 50px;padding-bottom: 50px;padding-left: 50px;} .ffb-id-48t2hql8{ text-align: center;}.ffb-id-48t2hqlc{ padding-top: 50px;padding-right: 50px;padding-bottom: 50px;padding-left: 50px;}.ffb-id-48t2hqlc ,.ffb-id-48t2hqlc:before,.ffb-id-48t2hqlc:after,.ffb-id-48t2hqlc *,.ffb-id-48t2hqlc *:before,.ffb-id-48t2hqlc *:after{ color: #797979 !important;}.ffb-id-48t2hqlc{ font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;}.ffb-id-48t2hqlc:before,.ffb-id-48t2hqlc:after,.ffb-id-48t2hqlc:hover,.ffb-id-48t2hqlc:focus,.ffb-id-48t2hqlc *,.ffb-id-48t2hqlc *:before,.ffb-id-48t2hqlc *:after,.ffb-id-48t2hqlc *:hover,.ffb-id-48t2hqlc *:focus{ font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;}.ffb-id-48t2hqlc{ font-size: 16px !important;line-height: 24px !important;fon